{"tid":950091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西安拆裝飾禁慶祝聖誕節","createTime":"2018-12-21T09:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T11:27:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"77572574ba820d38aa866bf0094139b062d56388","tid":950091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181221/20573510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F20573510&d=KMFAk3JdVptrirVU0BTG%2B4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3a8b94d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F20573510&h=97bd9d79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181221/20573510</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月21日 <br />\n<br />\n西安拆裝飾禁慶祝聖誕節<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181221/large/a1903a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181221%2Flarge%2Fa1903a.gif&h=1d49b7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地商場去年仍有慶祝聖誕節。<br />\n<br />\n一年一度聖誕節將至，中共又出招抗拒「西方文化入侵」。繼去年出手打壓聖誕等西方節日，中國各地今年繼續頒佈聖誕節禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁懸掛聖誕襪戴聖誕帽<br />\n<br />\n繼地處京畿的河北省廊坊市後，陝西西安也傳出消息，當局發出禁止慶祝聖誕節的通知，指明娛樂場所禁止一切聖誕節有關的裝飾和活動，已懸掛的要自行拆除，意味地方政府要全面抹去西方節日的存在。<br />\n<br />\n根據內地社交網上最新流傳的對話截圖顯示， 西安市鼓樓派出所近日發通知，轄區內的酒店、卡拉OK、網吧及人員密集所、酒店等「禁止一切聖誕節有關的裝飾和活動」；禁止懸掛聖誕襪、佩戴聖誕帽、擺放聖誕樹等一切與聖誕節有關的活動。如果已經懸掛，要限時自行拆除。<br />\n<br />\n同時，河北廊坊市城管局近日發通告，不准商店在街道擺放聖誕樹或裝飾，或舉行聖誕促銷活動，平安夜對小販出售聖誕襪、聖誕老人公仔進行大力打擊。韓國《朝鮮日報》指，習近平曾提出「倡導中國文明的偉大復興」；此後內地有關聖誕節的報道不見蹤影。中共喉舌《環球時報》報道，廊坊不是要禁止聖誕節，而是為了在中共宣傳部組織的每年一次的「全國文明城市」評選中得分。<br />\n<br />\n微信  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n圖圓習世盃夢　當選國腳年薪增20%"},{"pid":"5bffc57c713a4401b97b07f0c225f3a310ea35f3","tid":950091,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4471c8b491de741130faaebabf82cd4a8392cd7","tid":950091,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"鄰國已經只可以慶祝習誕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32522a2f13a90837db7cac2fff51134e8f4f0f50","tid":950091,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄰國<span style=\"color: red;\">以後</span>只可以慶祝習誕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3133595d0a0b91c1f5a6f284860bee09e2ae5477","tid":950091,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:14:10.000Z","msg":"要幾自卑先可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb61cb74bd4fc40cd2508a3e30ff8b11ffab6ac","tid":950091,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32522a2f13a90837db7cac2fff51134e8f4f0f50","tid":950091,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄰國<span style=\"color: red;\">以後</span>只可以慶祝習誕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"習大大~習大大~習總all the way~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34af2e11817991014f2748cff3405518d73a550c","tid":950091,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d13b94f948e11df1414deba1c109e97ffc7c9b","tid":950091,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34af2e11817991014f2748cff3405518d73a550c","tid":950091,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla